Package com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatteryObserver
    Listens to battery events in the way Android recommends it, which is listening to Intent.ACTION_BATTERY_LOW and Intent.ACTION_BATTERY_OKAY events.
    BatteryObserver.AggregateBatteryClassification
    POJO for tracking BatteryLevelEvent.BatteryStateClassification for both mobile and wearable device types, to be used as this Observer's observable type.
    EngineStateObserver
    Responsible for keeping track of the engine state in the DialogLib.
    EngineStateObserverTest
    Very basic tests for EngineStateObserver.
    EventObserver<Observable>
    Abstract implementation of a simple Observer, that allows for quick and thread safe implementations of observers/caches that keep track of data reported asynchronously.
    ObserverTest
    Abstract class that EventObserver tests should inherit from which will set up the test Looper.
    VerbosityLevelObserver
    An observer for verbosity level updates.
    VerbosityLevelObserverTest
    Tests VerbosityLevelObserver.
    WorkoutChoiceObserver
    Responsible for keeping track of the workout choice in the DialogLib.
    WorkoutSessionObserver
    Cache for WorkoutStateUpdates provided by ARDA during a workout in progress.
    WorkoutSessionObserver.WorkoutInfo
    Wrapper for relevant workout session information.
